    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Right, I have no data on this point. We'll see when the time comes.\n\nNevertheless, my first point still holds. If we provide a list of elements, we should use the correct markup for it. As a user, I expect plugins to generate correct markup, one that I could easily style. And having semantic markup is way better than `div`.\n",
